productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Cote d'Ivoire and I bought one.
i use it never again when i'm in my station.
My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
one of my hobbies is skydiving. and when i'm skydiving this works great.
i use it daily when i'm in my courthouse.
